Why Errors Happened (Normal on Windows)

pdf2image needs Poppler

pytesseract needs Tesseract

Python packages â‰  system binaries

Once Poppler + Tesseract were installed, everything worked.

Important Notes

OCR quality is good for theory text

Equations and symbols may be noisy

Diagrams are not extracted

OCR is done once, not repeatedly

